      "Text": "Security update for mariadb",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for mariadb fixes the following issues:\n\nUpdate to version 10.11.11.\n\n- CVE-2025-21490: vulnerability allows high privileged attacker with network access to cause hangs and frequent crashes\n  on affected servers (bsc#1243356).\n",
